This task is a thin layer on top of the toast lib: the install mutation from `useInstallPackage` is short-lived (the HTTP call either succeeds or fails), so for now the "progress" toast is just a pending spinner toast with the mutation's state. Real progress streaming is out of scope for this spec — if the spec 02 API adds SSE progress events later, wire them here.

