- Shows "Update to vX.Y.Z" button when `updateAvailable` is true
- "Uninstall" click enters confirm mode (3-second window) before firing mutation
- Uses `purge: true` for uninstall (this flow assumes the user wants to fully remove)
- Empty state when nothing is installed
- Loading skeleton reuses `PackageLoadingSkeleton` with `count={3}`

